title: "Blue Bloods'" Bridget Moynahan Shares Photos from Her Wedding Day
text:
"Blue Bloods'" Bridget Moynahan Shares Photos from Her Wedding Day Posted just a moment ago 
Craig Blankenhorn /CBS (NEW YORK) -- Blue Bloods actress Bridget Moynahan is officially off the market. 
On Saturday evening, the actress tied the knot with New York businessman Andrew Frankel in an intimate ceremony in the Hamptons, reports People . 
Moynahan posted multiple photos of the ceremony to her Instagram account. "Oh, by the way, guess what I just did," the actress captioned one of the photos. 
A photo posted by Bridget Moynahan (@bridgetmoynahan) on Oct 17, 2015 at 5:36pm PDT 
Another photo posted by the bride shows Moynahan being escorted down the aisle by her father, Edward Bradley Moynahan. "I love you Dad," the actress wrote in the caption . 
A photo posted by Bridget Moynahan (@bridgetmoynahan) on Oct 18, 2015 at 3:36pm PDT 
This is Moynahan's first marriage. The actress was previously linked to New England Patriots' Tom Brady, and the former couple have an eight-year-old son.
